- First Test

    # File test_one.py
    def test_passing():
        assert (1, 2, 3) == (1, 2, 3)
    def test_failing():
        assett (1, 2, 3) == (3, 2, 1)


    # Run tests
    $ pytest test_one.py
    $ pytest -v test_one.py



- Installing pytest

    pip install pytest